(46, 'Wynton Microfiber Reversible 3 Piece Comforter Set', 'wynton-microfiber-reversible-3-piece-comforter-set', 15, 21, '1660828567-1.jpg,1660828567-2.jpg,1660828567-3.jpg', '<p>Nice double stitching overclock with piping not only makes the down alternative comforter set elegant and luxurious but also makes the seams stronger than single-needle stitching and prevents the allergy-free fiberfill from escaping the comforter. The baffle box construction crafted with high-density needle stitching prevents the fiberfill from shifting, even after a wash.</p>\r\n<p>What\'s Included?</p>\r\n<p>2 Shams</p>\r\n<p>Comforter</p>\r\n<p>Accent Pillow</p>\r\n<p>Features</p>\r\n<p>No annoying mess-up trouble after wash. By applying special treated high-quality fiberfill and sewing-stitching crafts, the shape keeps well even after many washes.</p>\r\n<p>No quality-worry problem. By using high-quality certified materials on fabric and filling, the comforter has greater longevity than your expectations.</p>\r\n<p>Available in Twin, Queen, King and Oversized King Sizes. The twin set includes 1 comforter (68&rdquo; x 92&rdquo;) And 2 shams (20&rdquo; x 26&rdquo;+ 2&rdquo;); the Queen set includes: 1 comforter (90&rdquo; x 92&rdquo;) And 2 shams (20&rdquo; x 26&rdquo;+ 2&rdquo;); King set includes: 1 comforter (104&rdquo; x 92&rdquo;) And 2 shams (20&rdquo; x 30&rdquo;+ 2&rdquo;); Oversize King set includes: 1 comforter (116&rdquo; x 95&rdquo;) And 2 shams (20&rdquo; x 36&rdquo;+ 2&rdquo;). Please note orange color King shams size: (20&rdquo; x 36&rdquo;+ 2&rdquo;)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 77.99, 41.77, 42, 'default', 'active', '2022-08-18 09:16:51', '2022-09-30 10:48:55'),
(47, 'Lumberjack by 6ix Tailors Fine Linens', 'lumberjack-by-6ix-tailors-fine-linens', 15, 21, '1660827225-1660670994.jpg,1660827225-1660670995.jpg,1660827225-1660670996.jpg,1660827225-1660671001.jpg,1660827225-1660671002.jpg', NULL, 1440.00, NULL, 803, 'new', 'active', '2022-08-18 11:53:45', '2022-08-18 11:53:45'),
(48, 'Favo by Sferra Fine Linens', 'favo-by-sferra-fine-linens', 15, 21, '1660828018-123873.jpg,1660828018-1520967026.jpg,1660828018-1520967040.jpg,1660828018-1520967060.jpg,1660828018-1520967076.jpg', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.3em; color: #7c8990; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Favo by Sferra Fine Linens is timeless and lovely with a glorious honeycomb like design. The pique matelasse design of the Favo adds a classic touch to the bed. Favo coverlets and shams are finished with a flange. Made of 100 percent Egyptian cotton, the Favo collection is made in Italy to exacting standards. Favo is available in coverlets from Twin to King, boudoir shams, standard pillow shams, king pillow shams, and euro pillow shams. Also offered are bedskirts with a 21 inch drop. Your choice of colors including Charcoal, Ivory, Latte, White. Machine washable following manufacturers directions.</p>\r\n<div class=\"product-specs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid #424a4f; padding: 0px; margin-top: 10px; color: #7c8990; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"product-specs-hdr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; background: #424a4f; color: #ffffff; padding: 3px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;\">Fabric Content:</span><span class=\"product-specs-details\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 12px;\">Fabric: 100% Egyptian Cotton. Made in Italy.</span><span class=\"product-specs-hdr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; background: #424a4f; color: #ffffff; padding: 3px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;\">Washing Instruction:</span><span class=\"product-specs-details\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 12px;\">Machine washable following manufacturers directions. Machine washable on gentle cycle, warm water. Non chlorine bleach as needed. Wash dark colors sep</span><span class=\"product-specs-hdr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; background: #424a4f; color: #ffffff; padding: 3px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;\">Delivery Time:</span><span class=\"product-specs-details\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 12px;\">1-2 Days</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 265.00, NULL, 13, 'featured', 'active', '2022-08-18 12:06:58', '2022-08-18 12:06:58'),
(49, 'Allegra by Sferra Fine Linens', 'allegra-by-sferra-fine-linens', 15, 21, '1660828277-34706.jpg', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.3em; color: #7c8990; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Allegra Blanket by Sferra Fine Linens is a luxurious addition to your bed. This gorgeous cotton twill is soft and comfortable, introducing a layer of softness and warmth beautifully. The Allegra features a stonewashed finish to create the perfect layer for the cooler months. Allegra blankets made of piece dyed textural weave and feature a two turned hem finish. Made in Portugal of 100 percent cotton. Allegra is available in blankets from Twin to King. Your choice of colors including Aloe, Aquamarine, Banana, Flint, Navy, and White. Machine washable following manufacturers directions.</p>\r\n<div class=\"product-specs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid #424a4f; padding: 0px; margin-top: 10px; color: #7c8990; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"product-specs-hdr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; background: #424a4f; color: #ffffff; padding: 3px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;\">Fabric Content:</span><span class=\"product-specs-details\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 12px;\">100% Cotton, Stonewashed</span><span class=\"product-specs-hdr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; background: #424a4f; color: #ffffff; padding: 3px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;\">Washing Instruction:</span><span class=\"product-specs-details\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 12px;\">Machine Washable</span><span class=\"product-specs-hdr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; background: #424a4f; color: #ffffff; padding: 3px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;\">Delivery Time:</span><span class=\"produc