(64, 'Danby 3-in-1 Portable Air Conditioner - 9000 BTU (SACC 5000 BTU)', 'danby-3-in-1-portable-air-conditioner-9000-btu-sacc-5000-btu', 16, 11, '1661173331-15069284.jpg,1661173331-15069284_1.jpg,1661173331-15069284_2.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: #31383b; font-family: \'Human BBY\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Keep your room comfortable regardless of the weather outside with the Danby 3-in-1 portable air conditioner. With a 9,000 BTU capacity, 2 powerful fan speeds, and two-directional air flow, you can efficiently cool spaces up to 150 sq. ft. It also includes a dehumidifier mode with direct drain for continuous operation and optimal moisture removal.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"bodyContainer_lmm4I down_1fxZR\" style=\"padding: 0px; -webkit-box-ordinal-group: 3; order: 2; color: #ffffff; font-family: \'Human BBY\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"container_G-fMB\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: height 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1) 0s;\">\r\n<div class=\"body_maqiI down_1fxZR open_2zRYc\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: none;\">\r\n<div id=\"moreInfo\" class=\"productInfoContainer_3eV0T tabItemContainer_3agCS displayBlock_2eUV1 fullWidth_1yFPz\" style=\"width: 1280px; padding: 0px 24px 32px; border-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" data-automation=\"pdp-more-information-tab\">\r\n<div class=\"moreInformation_1u1Nn\" style=\"display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: justify; justify-content: space-between;\">\r\n<div class=\"productDescription_2WBlx\" style=\"line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 16px 24px; color: #31383b; width: 739.188px;\">\r\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 32px; margin: 0px auto;\">\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 8px; font-size: 16px; list-style: disc;\">Three-in-one portable design includes built-in air conditioning, fan, and dehumidifier modes to ensure optimal comfort in your room</li>\r\n<li style=\"line-height: 