(72, 'Evil Offering V2 Bike GX', 'evil-offering-v2-bike-gx', 17, 8, '1661175178-10531884x1233480_zm.jpg', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #070a0c; font-family: Catamaran, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">If Evil&rsquo;s Following is the short travel trail slayer and the Wreckoning is our leg-powered DH legend, then the Offering is the all-arounder twenty-niner. It spins up like a tornado and descends with playful fury. Evil&rsquo;s geometry stays shred-ready for all riders. No matter where you live or how you pedal, Evil&rsquo;s bikes feature built-in adjustability to elevate your ride. And it&rsquo;s all thanks to the Flip Chip. Switching the orientation of the Flip Chip provides a 2.1-degree spectrum of change covering every style of riding from laid-back to aggressive. Flip it to LOW and the Offering is ready to ride in a trail-happy, fast-handling capacity. Or opt for the X-LOW position to drop the bottom bracket 11 millimeters and slacken the head tube angle for increasing stability and confidence in steeper terrain and higher speeds. Offering does it all.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #070a0c; font-family: Catamaran, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Want more flexibility? With Evil\'s aftermarket angle set, an additional four positions become available, allowing for a total of six potential configurations. Ride the Offering in the stock (LOW) orientation with ultra-efficient forward pedaling position, or in X-LOW with an aftermarket slack 1.5-degree angle set to increase your comfort zone in the steeps. Flip Chips place the rider where the rider wants to be.</p>', 5999.00, 4784.79, 53, 'default', 'active', '2022-08-22 12:32:58', '2022-08-22 12:32:58'),
(73, '20 Inch Mountain Bike Kids Steel 21 Speed Dual Disc Brakes and Front Suspension', '20-inch-mountain-bike-kids-steel-21-speed-dual-disc-brakes-and-front-suspension', 17, 8, '1661259148-1.jpg,1661259149-2.webp,1661259149-3.webp', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; padding: 0px; color: #2e3538; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, SimSun; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700 !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 24px;\">Great for your child\'s first bike</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; padding: 0px; color: #2e3538; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, SimSun; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\">Entry-level option, durable steel frame and disc, ready for city and off-road.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; padding: 0px; color: #2e3538; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, SimSun; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2g0o.detail.1000023.i0.18296c31EkqJ2v\">Perfect for riders who want to challenge all kinds of terrain. The steel frame provides durability for those tough courses. The wheels feature lightweight-strength alloy rims and all-terrain tires. From sidewalks to trails, go out and ride with your buddies and enjoy the freedom of riding.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700 !important;\">About this project</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\">From the pavement to the trails, go out and ride with your buddies; the combination of an aluminum mountain frame and suspension fork provides a durable and responsive ride on a variety of terrains</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\">Shifter and rear derailleur for smooth, precise shifting on virtually any road surface or slope</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\">Front and rear alloy linear brakes provide precise stopping power.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\">The wheels feature alloy rims that are lightweight and all-terrain tires provide a long-lasting ride.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; padding: 0px; color: #2e3538; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, SimSun; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-word; font-size: 20px;\">The 20\" is a steel mountain bike for everyone, with front suspension and disc brakes.</span></p>', 178.40, NULL, 364, 'new', 'active', '2022-08-23 11:52:29', '2022-10-07 18:26:48'),
(74, 'ORBEA AVANT H30-D ENDURANCE ROAD BIKE (60CM)', 'orbea-avant-h30-d-endurance-road-bike-60cm', 17, 8, '1661259477-m10260bi.jpg,1661259477-m10260bj.jpg,1661259477-m10360bh.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\">The Orbea Avant is designed to help riders thoroughly enjoy the long hours spent on the road. This endurance road bike is built around providing the best possible riding experience and boasts a quality component package and an entry level price point. The speed, freedom, and views offered by quiet roads are all included with the Avant for free.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Features:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 6px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li class=\"selected\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2rem; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hydroformed aluminum high-polish frame construction</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2rem; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Avant carbon fork provides balanced elasticity, tire clearance, and torsional stiffness</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2rem; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Integrated fender mounting points</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2rem; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Internal cable routing carefully routed along the best path with no rubbing or rattling</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 2rem; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Clearance for tires up to 35mm in width</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Specifications:</strong></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 6px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: \'univers lt std\', Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #070a0c; background-color: #ffffff; list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li class=\"selected\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>Frame:</strong>&nbsp;Orbea Avant Hydro Disc (BB68) (12 x 142mm)</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><s