(75, 'Cannondale TREADWELL EQ DLX - 27.5\" City Bike - 2022 - Black Magic', 'cannondale-treadwell-eq-dlx-275-city-bike-2022-black-magic', 17, 8, '1661259684-treadwell-eq-dlx-black-magic-2-1099335.jpg,1661259684-treadwell-eq-dlx-black-magic-1099334.jpg', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.21; margin: 1rem 0px 0.5rem; color: #3d4548; font-family: BlenderPro, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Nothing beats a bike ride.</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0px; color: #3d4548; font-family: BlenderPro, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Lots of fun and low weight - The Cannondale Treadwell is ideal to rip around the neighborhood for meet ups, running errands or Sunday fun days. It is comfortable, playful and above all easy to use. A powerful, well made bike and a tribute to the cool bikes of those days. With handlebars and tires that remind you of Dirt-Racer.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 1rem 0px 0px; color: #3d4548; font-family: BlenderPro, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">An integrated wheel sensor helps track your activity (like speed, distance and calories burned), registers your bike, reminds you of needed service and more, all through the free Cannondale app. With a convenient front and rear rack, lights and full-coverage fenders, Treadwell EQ DLX is ready to bring a little fun and extra versatility to the daily to and from.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.21; margin: 1rem 0px 0.5rem; color: #3d4548; font-family: BlenderPro, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Features of Cannondale TREADWELL EQ DLX:</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 1.125rem; margin: 1rem 0px; color: #3d4548; font-family: BlenderPro, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-colo